---
description: Version and metadata management
globs: "pyproject.toml,pdd/__init__.py,CHANGELOG.md"
alwaysApply: false
---
- Follow semantic versioning (major.minor.patch)
- Keep version numbers synchronized across:
  - pyproject.toml
  - pdd/__init__.py
  - README.md
  - shell completion scripts
  - Other version references
- Use commitizen for version bumping
- Document all significant changes in CHANGELOG.md
- Include appropriate metadata in package information
